            <title>[FLINK-28085] Close all the pending Pulsar transactions when flink shutdown the pipeline.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-28085</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently transactionId is not persisted. After a job restart we lose handle to the transaction which is still not aborted in Pulsar broker. Pulsar broker will abort these hanging transactions after a timeout but this is not desirable. We need to close all the pending transactionId.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
